Titolo: RalliSport Challenge 2

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: RalliSport Challenge 2 is a 2004 rally racing video game, and the sequel to 2002â€™s RalliSport Challenge. This game contains new features such as a cockpit cameras and ability to change car at the last moment. However, stats like total horsepower and number of gears have been eliminated from the car selection screen.
Cars are split up into five categories with two subcategories each plus "Classic" cars. There are four paint schemes on each car and drivers must drive 31, 87, and 249 miles before unlocking a new one. By winning all championships in the career mode, all paint schemes for all cars are unlocked.

Genere: Racing 

Valutazione: N/A
